辅导员	食堂
assistance provision, institutional guidance<SEP>institutional referral, assistance channel
The cafeteria advises contacting the class counselor to help address needs that it cannot fulfill directly.<SEP>The cafeteria directs users to contact the counselor as an alternative when they cannot fulfill requests for pet food.

宠物食品	食堂
service limitation, procurement barrier
The cafeteria is unable to produce pet food, necessitating alternatives.

网购	食堂
alternative recommendation, digital procurement
The cafeteria suggests using online shopping as an alternative method for acquiring unavailable items like pet food.

宠物食品	网购
e-commerce solution, product acquisition
Online shopping serves as a procurement method for acquiring the unavailable category of pet food.

宠物食品	辅导员
need fulfillment, service mediation
The class counselor assists in resolving requests related to the unattainable pet food category.

学生	督察队
permission contrast, access restriction
学生被允许就餐而督察队禁止，体现不同群体的权限差异

校长	督察队
prohibited group, exclusion policy
两者均被禁止在食堂就餐，并构成触发他人离开的共同条件

学生	校长
exclusion trigger, emergency response
当学生发现校长在食堂点餐时必须立即离开并暂停24小时到访

督察队	老师
compliance requirement, access conflict
教师可正常就餐但需遵守当督察队出现时的撤离指令

学生	本食堂
authorized access, venue permission
学生被允许在本食堂正常就餐，体现场所授权关系

本食堂	老师
equal access rights, staff benefits
教师享有与学生相同的食堂用餐权限

本食堂	督察队
exclusion trigger, prohibited entry
督察队进入食堂会触发其他用餐者立即离开的强制性规则

本食堂	校长
access violation, emergency evacuation
校长在食堂出现时，场所规则要求所有用餐人员必须撤离并暂停24小时到访

学生	老师
shared privileges, policy compliance
两者共享相同的食堂使用权限且受相同行为规范约束

学院食堂	督察部
政策执行, 监督管理<SEP>监督管理, 政策落实
督察部监督学院食堂的运营，确保其政策执行并处理违规投诉。<SEP>督察部监督学院食堂的运营，确保其遵守不强制限制饮食选择的规定，并处理相关违规投诉。

学生会	学院食堂
政策冲突, 违规行为
学生会若组织成员要求师生前往指定位置打饭，则违反学院食堂的自选制政策，需通过督察部处理。

学生会	督察部
违规监督, 纠纷处理
当学生会的行为违反规定时（如强制指定打饭地点），督察部负责介入调查并解决此类违规问题。

学院食堂	餐饮自由选择政策
政策实施, 权利保障
学院食堂运营基于该政策，确保师生饮食选择权不受侵犯。

学生会	指定位置打饭事件
违规行为来源, 政策冲突
学生会若强制要求成员前往特定地点用餐，则直接引发此类违规事件的发生。

学院食堂	老师
权利行使, 违规监督
教师作为食堂用户，需遵守自选制政策；若其强制指定打饭地点则构成对政策的违反。

同学	督察部
权益保护, 纠纷解决
当学生遭遇违规行为（如被强制指定打饭）时，可直接联系督察部寻求帮助。

指定位置打饭事件	督察部
事件处置, 监督机制
督察部是处理此类强制行为的核心部门，负责调查和解决相关纠纷。

学生/同学	督察部
supervision, enforcement reporting<SEP>supervision, reporting
Students must report non-compliant brands to the Supervision Department for action.<SEP>Students must report non-compliant brands to the Supervision Department.

品牌	督察部
inspection, oversight
When a brand resumes operations, the Supervision Department checks its health records and signs off for safety confirmation.

品牌	学院食堂
location containment, operational dependency<SEP>location-based operation, facility dependency
Brands are food service providers located within the college canteen.<SEP>Brands operate as food service providers within the college canteen facility.

品牌重新恢复工作	督察部
event trigger, regulatory enforcement
The Supervision Department must conduct health inspections during brand resumption events to ensure safety compliance.

卫生表	品牌重新恢复工作
reopening criteria, safety verification<SEP>safety compliance, documentation requirement
A valid and recently signed health report is mandatory for a brand to resume operations after closure.<SEP>A valid health inspection report with recent signatures from the Supervision Department must be present when a brand resumes operations after closure.

卫生表	品牌
compliance dependency, health monitoring<SEP>compliance dependency, safety certification
Brands are required to maintain up-to-date health inspection reports signed by the Supervision Department for operational approval.<SEP>Each brand is required to maintain valid health inspection reports signed by the Supervision Department for operational approval.

卫生表	督察部
10
The Supervision Department validates brand compliance by signing health inspection reports.<"|>"regulatory authority, documentation validation

发现猫或狗在食堂	督察部
事件上报, 责任处置
当发生动物出现在食堂事件时，必须立即向督察部报告以启动处理流程

发现猫或狗在食堂	食堂
场所关联, 空间定位
该事件的发生地点限定在食堂地理区域范围内

卫生	发现猫或狗在食堂
安全威胁, 卫生干预
动物出现在餐饮区直接构成公共卫生风险，要求采取清洁措施

发现猫或狗在食堂	就餐安全
安全指令, 应急响应<SEP>紧急处置, 行为指导
动物出现事件触发必须暂停就餐的安全指令<SEP>动物出现直接触发必须放弃用餐的紧急处置措施

卫生	就餐安全
协同保障, 安全体系
公共卫生维护与用餐安全措施共同构成应急响应的核心要素

督察部	督察部同学
隶属关系, 职责关联
督察部同学是该组织在食堂现场执行任务的具体责任人

督察部	食堂
场所管辖, 监督职责
督察部对食堂区域内的突发事件负有监管和处理责任

外卖服务	学院食堂
service provider, delivery limitation<SEP>service provision, policy adherence
The campus canteen offers takeout delivery service to designated dormitories.<SEP>The canteen provides takeout services under the constraints defined by its distribution policy.

1-4号宿舍楼	外卖服务
location restriction, service availability
The takeout service is exclusively delivered to dormitory buildings 1-4.

学院食堂	食堂自取服务
alternative service, policy enforcement
The campus canteen provides self-pickup as an alternative for orders outside approved delivery zones.

外卖配送政策	学院食堂
policy enforcement, service control<SEP>policy enforcement, service regulation
The campus canteen enforces the takeout delivery restriction policy.<SEP>The campus canteen enforces this policy to regulate takeout delivery availability.

1-4号宿舍楼	外卖配送政策
location restriction, policy implementation
The policy mandates that takeout services are exclusively delivered to these dormitory buildings.<SEP>The policy mandates that takeout services are only available to dormitory buildings 1-4.

外卖配送政策	食堂自取服务
alternative service requirement, compliance<SEP>alternative service, compliance requirement
The policy requires customers outside approved locations to use self-pickup instead of delivery.<SEP>The policy requires customers to use self-pickup when orders are placed outside approved locations.

外卖服务	外卖配送政策
service limitation, regulatory control
The policy restricts where takeout delivery is permitted, limiting it to specific dormitories.

学生守则	学院
policy enforcement, institutional authority<SEP>regulation enforcement, policy implementation
The Academy enforces the Student Code of Conduct as part of its institutional policies.<SEP>The Academy enforces the Student Code of Conduct to maintain order and hygiene across campus.

学院	食堂建议
campus governance, institutional goals<SEP>policy dissemination, institutional authority
The Academy issued the Dining Hall Notice to maintain campus hygiene and enforce student conduct rules.<SEP>The Academy supports the Dining Hall Notice as part of its broader effort to ensure campus hygiene through student compliance.

学生守则	食堂建议
regulation enforcement, compliance<SEP>regulation reinforcement, policy implementation
The Dining Hall Notice directly references and reinforces specific provisions of the Student Code of Conduct.<SEP>The Dining Hall Notice serves as a specific implementation of the broader Student Code of Conduct.

学院	食堂
institutional oversight, facility management
The Academy oversees the Dining Hall as one of its operational facilities responsible for student welfare.

食堂	食堂建议
policy dissemination, facility responsibility
The Dining Hall issued the notice to reinforce compliance with Academy policies regarding food consumption areas.
